# ============================================================================
# WorldModelData Universal Gaming Ontology v1 â€” COMPOSED ENTRYPOINT
#
# Purpose:
# - Provide a single ontology entrypoint that imports:
#   - the flagship universal gaming ontology distribution, and
#   - optional extension modules.
#
# This avoids expanding the core universal namespace prematurely while still
